{"data":[{"name":"97:1","price":"እኛ (ቁርኣኑን) በመወሰኛይቱ ሌሊት አወረድነው፡፡ {1}","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنزَلۡنَٰهُ فِي لَيۡلَةِ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6126,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"{1} ይህች ሌሊት በሮመዳን ውስጥ ትገኛለች ። በመጨረሻዎቹ አስርት ሌሊቶች ከነሱም በኢተጋማሽ ሌሊቶች በ21፣ 23፣ 25፣ 27፣ 29 ውስጥ ትገኛለች ። እርሷን በሶላትና በኢባዳ ያሳለፋ ሰው ያለፈው ሃጥአቱ ምህረት ይደረግለታል።","lang":"am","meta":{"transliteration":"innā anzalnāhu fī laylati al-qadri ","translations":["Indeed, We","revealed it","in","(the) Night","(of) Power","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","anzalnāhu","fī","laylati","al-qadri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2949],[2,2949,5469],[3,5469,5939],[4,5939,6759],[5,6759,7884]]}},{"name":"97:2","price":"መወሰኛይቱም ሌሊተ ምን እንደ ኾነች ምን አሳወቀህ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6127,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"am","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā laylatu al-qadri ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(the) Night","(of) Power (is)","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","laylatu","al-qadri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2130],[2,2130,3260],[3,3260,3670],[4,3670,4480],[5,4480,5945]]}},{"name":"97:3","price":"መወሰኛይቱ ሌሊት ከሺሕ ወር በላጭ ናት፡፡","arabic":"لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ خَيۡرٞ مِّنۡ أَلۡفِ شَهۡرٖ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6128,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"am","meta":{"transliteration":"laylatu al-qadri khayrun min alfi shahrin ","translations":["(The) Night","(of) Power","(is) better","than","a thousand","month(s)","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["laylatu","al-qadri","khayrun","min","alfi","shahrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1700],[3,1700,2380],[4,2380,3740],[5,3740,4300],[6,4300,5465]]}},{"name":"97:4","price":"በርሷ ውስጥ መላእክትና መንፈሱ (ጂብሪል) በጌታቸው ፈቃድ በነገሩ ሁሉ ይወርዳሉ፡፡","arabic":"تَنَزَّلُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ فِيهَا بِإِذۡنِ رَبِّهِم مِّن كُلِّ أَمۡرٖ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah